short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Sends native messages to Azentio Silent Print Application for Chromium

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension communicate with local application through native messaging to change windows printing parameters and make a silent print of documents.
